overview: Digital Impact Agency is a creative firm specializing in inbound marketing and interactive digital media strategies. We are a team of innovative entrepreneurs focused on creating the most strategic and effective communication channels for our client. The world has gone digital and we want to put your brand at the center of it. Online communication trends are continually changing and what was cool yesterday is just that - yesterday. To keep up, you need a marketing partner to be your eyes and ears in the digital world.
